Running this configuration you need some extra applications installed

I am using Arch Linux.
Between names and descirption, there are two kind lines like, - and --
- means you can download by pacman -S
-- means you can download by yaourt -S

i3-config
Edit what you don't need! like #statup area!
xfce4-terminal - Default terminal
dmenu - A menu for applications
i3lock - Lokc your screen
xorg-xkill - Force Kill applications
scrot - Screeshot

i3 bar conky:
alsa-utils - Volume Control
light-git -- Display Brightness
ttf-font-awesome -- Fonts may need
